Make sure you get this off with him.

340
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:11,630
刚才空气从房间两边的洞里往外跑
The air rushed out of holes on both sides of the room,

341
00:23:11,630 --> 00:23:13,610
这就意味着我们周围全是真空
Which means we're surrounded by a hard vacuum.

342
00:23:13,620 --> 00:23:14,780
我们被困住了
We're trapped.

343
00:23:15,170 --> 00:23:17,710
或许...或许我们可以强行打开这扇门
Maybe... maybe we can force the door.

344
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:19,810
-火星的密封门非常牢固 你知道的
- Mars builds too well, you know that.

345
00:23:19,810 --> 00:23:22,720
就算打开我们也得完蛋 我们没有太空服
We'd still be screwed because we don't have our pressure suits.

346
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:26,160
大气循环系统还坏着
Atmosphere systems are still out.

347
00:23:26,650 --> 00:23:28,930
我估计我们还剩大约20分钟的空气
I figure we have maybe 20 minutes of air left.

348
00:23:28,930 --> 00:23:30,110
糟透了
Crap!

349
00:23:33,030 --> 00:23:34,180
你在干什么
What're you doing?

350
00:23:35,130 --> 00:23:36,330
镇静剂
Sedative.

351
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:38,340
这里面的量足够镇静我们中的一个
There's enough here to take one of us out,

352
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:39,730
延缓这个人的呼吸
which will slow down their breathing

353
00:23:39,730 --> 00:23:41,510
减少我们的氧气消耗
and cut down our oxygen use.

354
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:44,200
-或许能多争取一点时间 -做什么的时间
- Maybe buy us a little more extra time. - For what?

355
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,540
你以为会有人来救我们吗
You think someone's going to come and get us?

356
00:23:45,540 --> 00:23:47,420
我们没有通讯器 没法求救
We don't have comms, we can't call for help.

357
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:48,850
你有更好的计划吗
Do you got a better plan?

358
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,650
这是我的主意 我来
It's my idea. I'll take the shot.

359
00:23:50,650 --> 00:23:52,710
不行 我们需要你保持清醒
No! We need you conscious.

360
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:55,510
他是地球人 他用的氧气最多 该让他来
He's an Earther, he uses the most air. He should do it!

361
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:57,740
我能背得动你 你背不动我
I can carry you. You can't carry me.

362
00:24:00,420 --> 00:24:01,610
该死
Damn it.

363
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:12,740
我希望能醒过来
I wanna wake up.

364
00:25:06,530 --> 00:25:07,980
我想谢谢你
I want to say thank you.

365
00:25:10,110 --> 00:25:11,080
你明白的
You know,

366
00:25:12,990 --> 00:25:15,100
为你一直以来对我的帮助
for helping me all those times you did.

367
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:20,750
你是个好人
You're a good person.

368
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:25,780
我本可以做个更好的人的
I could've been better.

369
00:25:30,970 --> 00:25:32,870
我都没来得及说再见
I didn't even get to say goodbye.

370
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:36,500
对谁说
To who?

371
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:40,520
不重要了
It doesn't matter.

372
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:10,680
你知道最让我郁闷的是什么吗
You know what really chaps my ass?

373
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,830
我的船在受攻击 我的弟兄们在死去
The fact that I'm here protecting some lousy Earth taker

374
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:13,910
而我却在这里
while my ship's getting pounded

375
00:26:13,910 --> 00:26:14,870
保护一个恶心的地球无赖
and my buddies are dying.

376
00:26:14,870 --> 00:26:17,710
那你为什么不去帮他们 让我去帮我的人
Then why don't you go help them and let me go help mine.

377
00:26:17,710 --> 00:26:20,490
我们有命令在身 在火星上职责是有意义的
We have our orders. Duty means something on Mars.

378
00:26:20,490 --> 00:26:22,100
我倒很高兴让你走
I'd be happy to let you go.

379
00:26:22,370 --> 00:26:24,280
我听说土卫九的事是你和你的朋友们干的
I heard you and your friends were responsible for Phoebe.

380
00:26:24,280 --> 00:26:27,040
我对土卫九一无所知 你怎么不干脆问他
I know nothing about Phoebe. Why don't you just ask him?

381
00:26:33,320 --> 00:26:34,300
后撤寻找掩护
Fall back and cover!

382
00:26:34,300 --> 00:26:37,040
霍顿 后撤躲在我们身后 蹲下
Holden! Get back and stay back! And stay down!

383
00:26:59,820 --> 00:27:02,980
霍顿 停下 见鬼 霍顿 回来
Holden, stop! God damn it, Holden! Get back here!

384
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:19,800
好了 我来了 什么事情重要到
Okay, I'm here. What's so important that I had to drop everything

385
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:20,930
让我放下手头的一切跑来这个破洞
and come to this hell hole?

386
00:27:21,050 --> 00:27:21,840
认识这家伙吗
Recognize this guy?

387
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:23,740
认识 你在广场上找到的尸体
Yeah. The stiff you found in the square.

388
00:27:23,740 --> 00:27:25,490
-我听说是起谋杀 -看看这个
- I heard it was a murder. - Look at this.

389
00:27:28,040 --> 00:27:30,660
好棒 你查出他的身份了 工作就该这样
Great, you found his ID. That's how it's supposed to work.

390
00:27:30,660 --> 00:27:32,380
这不是他 看到了吗
It's not him, see.

391
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:35,040
每次我扫描这家伙 都出来一个不同的身份
Every time I sample the guy, I get a different ID comes up

392
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:35,950
约翰
亨特
地球
12区42层
男性

393
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:37,350
相貌看起来都吻合
with a face that looks like it could be a match.

394
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:37,620
杰里米
吉斯派尔
火星
12区42层
男性

395
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:40,460
这尸体有很多体内植入物
Your stiff's got a lot of implants.

396
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:42,530
我猜他有个身份欺骗设备模块
I bet he has an ID spoofer mod.

397
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:44,600
专门设计来弄晕警察们
They're designed to spin cops,

398
00:27:44,600 --> 00:27:46,100
让他们浪费时间追查错误的线索
waste their time chasing down false leads.

399
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:48,090
用这种东西的只有骗子们
The only guys who really use them are crooks.

400
00:27:48,250 --> 00:27:49,590
成功的骗子们 这东西可不便宜
Successful ones. They're not cheap.

401
00:27:49,590 --> 00:27:52,310
这些高科技的东西你一向比我强多了
You are way more of a gear-head than I ever was.

402
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:54,070
能帮我查出他的身份吗
Can you help me ID him?

403
00:27:54,070 --> 00:27:55,460
米勒 你有一个搭档来帮你做这些事
Miller, you have a partner for this kind of stuff.

404
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:57,900
我试过给哈弗洛克打电话 他不希望被人找
No, I tried Havelock, he didn't want to be found.

405
00:27:59,660 --> 00:28:01,610
我有时候也会这样
I've done the same from time to time.

406
00:28:04,510 --> 00:28:05,500
求你了
Please?

407
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:08,250
好吧
Well,

408
00:28:09,300 --> 00:28:10,080
如果他有欺骗设备
if he has a spoofer,

409
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:12,680
那他体内很可能还有一大堆违法的东西
then he's probably got a bunch of other shady shit in him.

410
00:28:12,690 --> 00:28:14,310
标准内耳麦克
Standard inner-ear mike,

411
00:28:15,100 --> 00:28:16,760
脊椎稳定器
spinal stabilizer,

412
00:28:16,230 --> 00:28:18,660
胰腺泵

413
00:28:16,910 --> 00:28:20,370
胰腺泵 普通型 给久坐的人用的
pancreatic pump, run of the mill, for the sedentary.

414
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:24,210
存储块

415
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:25,910
他腿里藏了一个存储块
He's got a memory crypt in his calf.

416
00:28:28,230 --> 00:28:29,310
我们把它拿出来
Let's take it out.

417
00:28:29,330 --> 00:28:31,080
-我去叫法医 -不要
- I'll get the coroner. - No.

418
00:28:32,390 --> 00:28:33,770
那家伙话太多了
That guy talks too much.

419
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,750
来吧
Here we go.

420
00:28:45,930 --> 00:28:46,770
寻找目标中

421
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:48,320
未抓取成功

422
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:58,950
寻找目标中

423
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:07,880
见鬼
Damn it.

424
00:29:09,410 --> 00:29:11,230
我又不会弄疼他
Well, it's not like I'm hurting the guy.

425
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:17,890
寻找目标中

426
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:18,430
抓取成功

427
00:29:18,460 --> 00:29:19,380
找到了
There.

428
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:21,630
成功
Bingo.

429
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:37,250
内容被加密了 当然
Content's encrypted, obviously.

430
00:29:37,300 --> 00:29:39,820
不过从文件名上看 应该是政府记录
But judging by the file names, these are government records.

431
00:29:39,820 --> 00:29:40,720
好吧
Okay.

432
00:29:40,780 --> 00:29:43,270
客户档案 公司研发...
Customs documents, corporate R&D...

433
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,720
这家伙是个数据倒卖贩
This guy was a data broker.

434
00:29:47,450 --> 00:29:48,900
不管他倒卖了什么
Well, whatever he brokered,

435
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:52,500
一定足够重要到害他丧命的地步
must have been important enough to get him killed.

436
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:55,350
-你有什么事没告诉我 -没有
- What're you not telling me? - Nothing.

437
00:29:55,820 --> 00:29:56,750
米勒
Miller.

438
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,330
你不知道比较好
It's better if you don't know.

439
00:30:02,010 --> 00:30:03,390
我不需要你来保护我
I don't need you to protect me.

440
00:30:03,390 --> 00:30:04,730
我没有保护你
I'm not protecting you.

441
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:08,930
我讨厌你这样做
I... I hate it when you do this.

442
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,840
谢谢了
Thanks.

443
00:30:17,340 --> 00:30:18,310
哈弗洛克
Havelock.

444
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,350
接电话啊
Come on.

445
00:30:22,660 --> 00:30:24,090
好吧 给他留言
All right. Leave him a message.

446
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:28,880
听着
Hey, look, um...

447
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,720
我不管你在干什么或者在干谁
I don't care if you're up to your whatever in whoever,

448
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:32,880
等你上来歇口气的时候
but when you come up for air,

449
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:36,120
我需要你帮我在沙迪那里打个掩护 好吗
I'm gonna need you to cover for me with Shaddid, okay?

450
00:30:36,120 --> 00:30:37,780
我没法跟你说细节
I can't give you any details,

451
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:40,840
你自己想象一下吧 好吗
but just use your imagination, all right?

452
00:30:40,990 --> 00:30:43,530
我知道只要你想 你很会做个卑鄙小人的
I know you can be a devious son of a bitch when you want to be.

453
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,590
我也会为你做同样的事的
I'd do the same for you.

454
00:30:55,620 --> 00:30:59,690
天啊 天啊 我去叫人帮忙
Oh shit! Shit! I'll get help!

455
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:02,940
来人救命啊 有一位警官需要帮助
Somebody help! This officer needs help!

456
00:31:04,330 --> 00:31:05,520
救命
Help me!

457
00:32:13,970 --> 00:32:17,020
放手 别逼我杀你
Let go. Don't make me shoot you.

458
00:32:17,170 --> 00:32:18,400
你不会的
You won't.

459
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:33,570
他的武器被盔甲锁定了 开不了枪的
His weapon is keyed to his armor, he couldn't have fired it.

460
00:32:33,570 --> 00:32:34,560
不用客气
You're welcome.

461
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:36,590
莫尔死了 混蛋
Mole's dead, asshole.

462
00:32:39,890 --> 00:32:44,700
对不起 真的很对不起 但除非你帮我
I'm sorry, I really am. But I won't testify to anything

463
00:32:45,210 --> 00:32:47,260
把我的朋友也带离这艘船 否则我不会作证
unless you help me get my friends off this ship.

464
00:32:47,260 --> 00:32:50,180
-闭嘴 我想对他问话 -遵命 长官
- Shut up. I want to speak to him. - Yes, sir.

465
00:32:51,450 --> 00:32:53,780
他看起来可不像我见过的那些外行星联盟大兵
He doesn't look like any OPA grunt I've ever seen.

466
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:56,100
这技术比他们先进多了
Tech is way too advanced.

467
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:57,480
他是你的了
Yours.

468
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:05,880
你为谁工作 你们为什么要毁掉坎特伯雷号
Who are you working for? Why did you destroy the canterbury?

469
00:33:06,780 --> 00:33:08,600
土卫九空间站 你在场吗
Phoebe Station. Were you there?

470
00:33:09,330 --> 00:33:12,290
你在场 发生了什么事
You were. What happened?

471
00:33:13,290 --> 00:33:14,560
认真听好了
Listen to me very carefully.

472
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:16,850
如果你想要医护人员来看你 就赶快交代
If you want medical attention, you start speaking now.

473
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:19,190
我们很快都会死了
We'll all be dead soon enough.

474
00:33:26,170 --> 00:33:27,240
-走吧 -拜托了
- Let's go. - Please.

475
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:29,400
你得帮我去救我的朋友们
You have to help me get my friends.

476
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,880
你也不会把自己人抛下不管的
You wouldn't leave one of yours behind.

477
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:32,910
我们是火星军人
We're Marines.

478
00:33:32,910 --> 00:33:35,420
我们发誓在必要的时候为他人牺牲
We've sworn to die for each other if we have to.

479
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,340
你都几乎不怎么了解他们
You barely know those other people.

480
00:33:37,350 --> 00:33:39,220
他们在这里完全是因为我
They're only here because of me.

481
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,240
我和你作笔交易
I'll make you a deal.

482
00:33:57,040 --> 00:33:58,600
谢德
Oh, Shed.

483
00:34:04,820 --> 00:34:06,170
你没事吧
Hey, are you okay?

484
00:34:09,910 --> 00:34:11,150
你回来了
You came back?

485
00:34:12,100 --> 00:34:12,910
当然
Of course I did.

486
00:34:12,910 --> 00:34:14,140
交易是这样的
The deal is this.

487
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:17,410
你们都要公开作证说火星
You will all testify that Mars had nothing to do

488
00:34:17,410 --> 00:34:19,290
与坎特伯雷号的毁灭无关
with the Canterbury's destruction.

489
00:34:19,650 --> 00:34:22,010
快穿好太空服 气封只是暂时性的
Suit up fast, the air seal is temporary.

490
00:34:22,010 --> 00:34:23,100
我们得快走
We have to move.

491
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:26,910
-亚历克斯怎么了 -他替大家挨了一针
- What's wrong with Alex? - He took one for the team.

492
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,570
我来背他
I'll carry him.

493
00:34:34,850 --> 00:34:37,370
来 伙计 穿上太空服
Come on, buddy. We gotta suit up.

494
00:34:41,730 --> 00:34:43,710
我们不能再被阻拦了
We can't get pinned down again,

495
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:45,650
我们得找到一条安全通往停机坪的路
we need a clear route to the hangar bay.

496
00:34:45,650 --> 00:34:48,310
我在努力 长官 但船上到处都是敌人
I'm trying, sir, but our ship is crawling with scumbags.

497
00:34:48,490 --> 00:34:49,690
洛佩兹
Lopez.

498
00:34:52,010 --> 00:34:53,060
听我说
Listen.

499
00:34:53,650 --> 00:34:55,320
我们都失去了我们在乎的人
We've all lost people we care about.

500
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:57,460
而且我对整件事情一头雾水
And I don't even have a clue as to why.

501
00:34:57,770 --> 00:34:59,480
但我不停地听到你们说起土卫九空间站
But I keep hearing about Phoebe Station.

502
00:34:59,490 --> 00:35:01,110
如果我们都要因为它死去
And if we're all going to die because of it,

503
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:03,580
你能至少告诉我那里到底发生了什么事吗
can't you at least tell me what the hell happened there?

504
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:06,930
土卫九空间站失去联系好几周
Donnager was dispatched to Phoebe Station

505
00:35:06,930 --> 00:35:09,050
唐纳吉尔号被派去查看
after she went silent for several weeks.

506
00:35:09,750 --> 00:35:10,720
为什么
Why?

507
00:35:11,510 --> 00:35:12,830
我们至今还是不知道
We still don't know.

508
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:16,950
上面所有人都死了 他们的尸体被烧成灰烬
Everyone on board was dead. Their bodies were incinerated.

509
00:35:16,950 --> 00:35:19,650
我们找到他们被重新冻入冰道的墙里
We found them re-frozen to the walls of the ice tunnels.

510
00:35:19,810 --> 00:35:21,350
我们以为是发生了火灾或者化学品泄露
We thought it was a fire or a chemical spill,

511
00:35:21,350 --> 00:35:24,530
但随后我们发现所有的电脑核心都被摧毁了
but then we discovered that all the computer cores were destroyed.

512
00:35:24,530 --> 00:35:26,490
你是说有人故意干的吗
You mean someone did it deliberately?

513
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:28,950
他们在掩盖什么事情
They were covering something up.

514
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:32,200
-什么事 -我不知道
- Like what? - I don't know.

515
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,670
老天
Jesus.

516
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:43,640
出什么事了
What happened?

517
00:35:44,550 --> 00:35:46,350
舰长启动了零号程序
The Captain has set Condition Zero.

518
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,620
她要炸掉这艘船
She's going to scuttle the ship.

