CIC and the bridge.

523
00:36:03,630 --> 00:36:05,220
准备好的备用舰离开停机坪了吗
Has the ready standby left the hangar bay?

524
00:36:05,220 --> 00:36:06,830
没有 长官 还在那里
Negative, sir. It's still there.

