Mag boots off. Move as fast as you can.

530
00:36:45,850 --> 00:36:48,970
所有人听我口令 等待掩护火力
Everybody on my mark. Standby for cover fire.

531
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:52,690
你可不许在我面前倒下
Hey, hey! Don't you quit on me.

532
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:55,280
好了
All right.

533
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:57,130
