What about the others?

538
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:54,210
都死了 我们得赶紧离开
They're gone. We have to dust off now.

539
00:39:10,090 --> 00:39:12,560
我不是飞行员 你得找别人来驾驶这艘船
I'm not a pilot. Someone else needs to fly.

