老大 我觉得我现在的状态...
Boss, I don't think I'm in any condition to...

544
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:36,610
-带我们离开 -没问题
- Get us out of here! - You got it.

545
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:42,610
我需要来些果汁
I need some juice.

546
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:57,330
好了 亲爱的 对我温柔点
Okay, sweetheart, be gentle with me.

547
00:39:58,060 --> 00:39:59,220
人家可是第一次
This is my first time.

548
00:40:35,200 --> 00:40:36,130
抱歉
Sorry.

549
00:40:43,870 --> 00:40:46,960
设定机动规避路线 最大速度
Evasive maneuvers. Max burn.

550
00:40:47,130 --> 00:40:49,030
别让任何人跟上我们
Do not let anyone stay on our tail.

551
00:40:49,610 --> 00:40:53,170
没问题 老大 我是说 遵命 长官
You got it, Hoss... I mean... Yes, sir.

552
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:03,200
要是能在火星上看到大海就好了
It would've been nice to see an ocean on Mars.

553
00:41:18,010 --> 00:41:19,810
-太刀号已经离开了 -长官
- The Tachi is away. - Sir.

554
00:41:20,390 --> 00:41:22,550
舰长 这扇门快撑不住了
Captain, this door won't hold much longer.

555
00:41:24,540 --> 00:41:26,240
我没想到我们会输
I didn't think we could lose.

556
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:55,060
我成功了 我成功了
I'm doing it. I'm doing it.

557
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:57,240
混蛋
Son of bitch.


